casebody.data:
Shannon ALEXANDER
v.
Darrell VANNOY, Warden, Louisiana State Penitentiary NO. 2018-KH-1556 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 29, 2019

Denied. Applicant shows no error by the lower courts, and has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review. See State v. Alexander, 18-0267 (La. 12/17/18), 259 So.3d 336.
